        <h3>Dive into the world’s biggest, boldest and best swim show!</h3>
        <p>Turning heads and turning out trends for more than three decades, SwimShow 2015 will be more comprehensive with a better than ever selection of the finest swimwear for women, men and children plus resortwear, beachwear, lifestyle, yoga and accessory collections from across the globe.</p>
        <p>This can’t-miss one-of-a-kind tradeshow offers exclusive access to the latest trends in swimwear, stunning sights and events, and a true celebration of the simple luxury of swimwear!</p>
